Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,本片开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有火腿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 真没礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 今天晚饭没问题?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢马铃薯炖肉对吧? 我会多做点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天20点会回来对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我先说 阿部喜欢开黄腔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人常被他开黄腔吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,若喝了酒 可能也会对圣子你开黄腔性骚扰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你就随便敷衍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 这个时间了 我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,早饭让你生气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,遭到老公上司侵犯的巨乳妻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,高桥 你真令人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这么好吃的饭 每天都在吃吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好羡慕 这么漂亮的太太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害啊胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫圣子?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这么会款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真羡慕啊 吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你说要介绍自豪的太太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想说是自豪太太的话那应该是美人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,若是丑女的话看你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是脸啊 是我喜欢的类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很完美 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿秀…我老公有工作很努力吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没给你添麻烦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊 被叫阿秀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫了阿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,阿秀工作很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是在当课长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,5年内职位就会并排了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要叫你高桥课长才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请饶了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,上次也是啊 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你能来下社长室吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,下个企划想拜托高桥你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不会亏待你啊 你来负责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,起来 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对课长很失礼吧 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,平常不会喝成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 我是高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请问是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,前几天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 因为是未知的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公发生了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…我老公发生了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,单刀直入的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们公司的商品 好像在背后用便宜价格卖出的样品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是跟业者挂勾呢 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,直接说的话 是业务上的盗领
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,犯了罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是发现我察觉到了呢 还是说是小看我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最近对我很冷淡啊他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊 我也不是要阻碍他出人头地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,都是男人 这种事该跟公司说呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是犯罪吧?犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过啊 也想保护你老公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊 若只是开除你老公的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不过啊 若扯上警察变成这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,闹上新闻的话 对你老公的职涯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好的话会要你们离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这很糟糕啊 能再来一杯吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎做才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧?那会担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太太啊 老实说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…可以对这件事不出声的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是…我也不是有想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 虽说还没放弃出人头地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说 我也进入了裁员名单里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,辞掉工作 也回到老家去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂太太你的心情 我懂弱者的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 要不出声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太太若你也能不出声的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 对我温柔点叫好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此都默不出声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是在瞧不起我吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 每个人都瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,把我当笨蛋 我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想做的话还是能做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 我就来做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要做就能做啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要不出声就好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你老公就惨了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,敢瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你活该啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要报警哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,报警?你报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,报了我就把全部的事说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我的话 没差哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的话有差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你报警啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看我怎么上你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想报警就报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我都说我不出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,盗领的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系吗?你老公
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,老公变犯罪者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我吸乳房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让我多做点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 住手 别太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,全都说出来没关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,盗领 犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是你老公哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 求你了 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我都说我不出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你就给我做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,让我上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴湿了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很棒的事吗?为了老公牺牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不出声就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要逃啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,站好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么住手 小穴很寂寞吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,湿答答啊小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就好好接受我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要让我做更过分的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,像是打你的 喜欢那种的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,像是这样 被掐脖的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你老公 就给我乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.31,0:23:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,给公司 也给你流出给媒体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那样也好啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.39,0:23:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪边啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我不出声吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.34,0:23:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的生活不想失去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话 就给我听话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,过来啊这边 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,知道要做什么好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,含啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.31,0:24:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你含啊 用自己的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.32,0:24:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会不出声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不要出声
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,给我好好服侍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.35,0:25:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,做啊自己的意识 含啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.38,0:25:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想要多含点啊 含啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.39,0:25:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,含啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.35,0:26:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我插入吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.30,0:26:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还要逃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.31,0:26:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌插入吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.31,0:26:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.40,0:26:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.34,0:27:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.29,0:27:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.38,0:27:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.31,0:27:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再给你插深点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.40,0:27:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.35,0:28:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.35,0:28:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再深点
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.42,0:28:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.36,0:28:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.30,0:28:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.37,0:28:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.37,0:28:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.33,0:29:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽 很爽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.33,0:29:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来吸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.37,0:29:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.37,0:29:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.31,0:29:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.33,0:30:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽 你也很爽吧?小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.42,0:30:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.36,0:30:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,插到深处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.32,0:31:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要让邻居看?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.33,0:31:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.33,0:31:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.40,0:31:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.33,0:31:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,去阳台好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.34,0:31:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很丢脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.29,0:31:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.38,0:32:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.35,0:32:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.30,0:33:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.40,0:33:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,自己翘起屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.34,0:33:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说请插进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.35,0:33:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只能那样做啊太太
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.42,0:33:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.29,0:34:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门能看更清楚点的翘起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.41,0:34:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.29,0:35:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.37,0:35:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干别人老婆受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.37,0:35:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我插深点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.31,0:35:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.34,0:35:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧?太太 说好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.35,0:36:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,若爽的话
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.30,0:36:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.39,0:36:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.33,0:36:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.42,0:37:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是在哭还是在爽啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.36,0:37:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.30,0:37:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.38,0:37:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.38,0:37:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.39,0:37:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.33,0:38:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.40,0:39:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.34,0:39:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要去报警也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.41,0:39:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不过会变怎样你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.42,0:39:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.29,0:39:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再来睋
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.38,0:40:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,圣子 没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.32,0:41:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可能感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.32,0:41:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有发烧吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.41,0:41:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,圣子 我爱你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.34,0:41:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.36,0:41:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来 老公 上次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.30,0:41:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你有话想说 是什么啊?你说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.31,0:42:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.31,0:42:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是圣子你不懂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.38,0:42:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.38,0:42:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也会吃完饭再回来 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.39,0:42:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.41,0:42:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.42,0:42:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,回来的吻呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.35,0:42:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我都回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.36,0:42:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,明明在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.36,0:42:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.30,0:43:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这么热我还特地来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.37,0:43:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,工作中流了这么多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.37,0:43:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,吻我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.38,0:43:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我生气吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.38,0:43:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的话啊 现在的生活会失去的你不知道吗:
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.39,0:43:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给我接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.40,0:43:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.41,0:43:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.41,0:43:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是早上的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.42,0:43:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,早上的吻已经做过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.42,0:43:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是晚上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.36,0:43:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上之吻 很色的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.36,0:44:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头 伸出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.38,0:44:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.38,0:44:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要什么啊?讨厌流汗的我?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.39,0:44:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那要一起洗澡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.39,0:44:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想就这样做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.33,0:44:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.34,0:44:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,会被邻居听到吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.35,0:44:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我是没差哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.42,0:45:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只要给我身体就好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.36,0:45:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.37,0:45:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以插入吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.37,0:45:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.37,0:45:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给我接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.38,0:45:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,开始湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.39,0:45:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.41,0:46:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.35,0:46:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别哭啊 都湿几次了啊这小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.36,0:46:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有小穴的昧道
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.31,0:46:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有淫荡小穴的味道 给我插入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.33,0:46:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.40,0:46:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.35,0:47:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.29,0:47:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再插深点
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.30,0:47:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,给你插到子宫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.38,0:47:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.39,0:47:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是在一个人爽什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.33,0:48:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,给我插入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.34,0:48:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽 很爽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.29,0:48:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.30,0:48:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.32,0:48:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.39,0:48:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.39,0:49:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.40,0:49:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.40,0:49:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这种的?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.41,0:49:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.35,0:49:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.36,0:49:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.37,0:49:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.31,0:49:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.40,0:50:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.41,0:50:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是在做晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.35,0:50:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,给心爱的老公
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.35,0:50:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.42,0:50:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.35,0:50:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.29,0:50:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.37,0:50:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真多汁啊就像太太
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.38,0:50:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,跟太太小穴的汁液一样很多啊这个番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.31,0:51:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.39,0:51:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.39,0:51:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.39,0:51:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我在后面无法做料理吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.34,0:51:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了啊 请你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.34,0:51:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.35,0:51:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.42,0:51:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒这么翘啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.29,0:51:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.38,0:52:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太太很诚实啊 一弄小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.32,0:52:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就马上扭来扭去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.39,0:52:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.40,0:52:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.33,0:52:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让我多玩点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.40,0:52:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.42,0:52:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 别太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.35,0:52:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.36,0:52:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而且太太啊 你只能听话
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.30,0:53:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不想失去这种生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.32,0:53:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想摸胸部就摸胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.32,0:53:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想吸就吸
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.39,0:53:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想插小穴就插入小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.39,0:53:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想射就射
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.40,0:53:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是那种关系吧?我们
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.34,0:53:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头翘起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.39,0:54:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 说不要做的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.33,0:54:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,已经知道是很爽的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.40,0:54:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为都做好几发了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.33,0:54:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.41,0:54:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很肿吧?我的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.42,0:54:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒很肿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.29,0:55:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说太太...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.37,0:55:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我多爱抚点?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.37,0:55:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.37,0:55:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要舔那里
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.33,0:55:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.35,0:56:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙 已经这么肿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.36,0:56:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来含啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.30,0:56:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.37,0:56:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.32,0:56:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,含啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.42,0:57:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.35,0:57:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,继续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.32,0:57:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.41,0:58:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,多品尝点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.37,0:58:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.38,0:58:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,用胸部夹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.32,0:58:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,用这么淫荡的胸部夹肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.40,0:59:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.34,0:59:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.42,0:59:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.36,0:59:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来爱抚啊 我的乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.30,0:59:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头 不让我爽的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.37,0:59:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这会变很糟糕的事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.32,1:00:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,吐囗水啊在我的肉棒上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.33,1:00:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.40,1:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吐在肉棒上啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.34,1:00:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.42,1:00:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.29,1:00:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有对老公做过?乳交
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.30,1:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.30,1:00:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 再多舔点胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.30,1:00:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.40,1:01:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.41,1:01:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快点射出来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.34,1:01:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想啊 想要我射出什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.41,1:01:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别问了 快点射
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.42,1:01:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不说不射哦 想要我射什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.42,1:01:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快点射出精子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.29,1:01:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真诱人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.37,1:01:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,还不射出来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.37,1:01:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为要请你多做点爽快的事
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.31,1:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想用太太的这里爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.32,1:02:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只用小穴做的才是乐趣吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.32,1:02:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.39,1:02:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,像刚一样对我的乳头舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.33,1:02:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽 也摸肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.34,1:02:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 好爽 肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.37,1:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.38,1:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚我舔了你的胸部
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.32,1:03:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,像那样子对两边的乳头舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.39,1:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,吸两边的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.34,1:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那样好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.34,1:03:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了快点射出来快点回去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.41,1:03:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你做就对了 我会射啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.30,1:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,边看我边做
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.31,1:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我射对吧?是从哪里射出啊?精子
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.31,1:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我在问你啊太太
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.32,1:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,从肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.39,1:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那再对肉棒多做点
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.33,1:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,睪丸里累积精子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.34,1:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,也来舔睪丸啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.38,1:05:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,用力握紧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.38,1:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,舔舔肉棒的前端
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.32,1:05:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,含进嘴里深处自己来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.41,1:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,再深点
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.30,1:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吐出来吧?太太
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.37,1:06:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,多用手和嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.31,1:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不然要插入小穴里哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.38,1:06:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再激烈点
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.40,1:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.41,1:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴小穴太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.42,1:07:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽的嘴小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.38,1:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.41,1:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开 让我看精子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.38,1:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,擦一擦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.33,1:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爽快多了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.35,1:09:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.42,1:09:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是不要吧?身体明明就有反应
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.36,1:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.30,1:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今天啊我带了好东西来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.31,1:09:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,会给你多爽点啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.38,1:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别抵抗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.32,1:10:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,其实啊被这样做边说不要的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.33,1:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是很享受吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.40,1:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.40,1:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴明明就湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.41,1:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有淫荡小穴的味道
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.36,1:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.36,1:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.36,1:10:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,带了好东西来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.36,1:10:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 住手 什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.30,1:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.37,1:10:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.31,1:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个太太的小穴会很爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.32,1:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.39,1:11:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行那样
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.33,1:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.35,1:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.30,1:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这里会变怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.38,1:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.34,1:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.34,1:12:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可以不用忍耐哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.35,1:12:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤都湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.35,1:12:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 不行再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.35,1:12:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是很爽才失禁的吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.36,1:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.30,1:13:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不要弄那里
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.32,1:13:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.40,1:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是去了在抖动吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.41,1:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来啊 内裤脱下来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.42,1:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你直接弄啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.42,1:13:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.29,1:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.30,1:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,已经湿答答了嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.38,1:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要那样看
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.39,1:14:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,会想仔细看啊小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.33,1:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.41,1:14:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.36,1:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.36,1:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 求你了 不行再做下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.40,1:15:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.41,1:15:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 快去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.30,1:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴很爽无计可施吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.38,1:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再让你多爽点啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.38,1:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.39,1:16:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒形状的玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.39,1:16:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把这插入到小穴深处
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.34,1:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,过来啊太太
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.35,1:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.35,1:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.42,1:17:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很想要
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.35,1:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.29,1:17:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,都湿了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.38,1:17:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴湿答答啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.39,1:17:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.39,1:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的爱液
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.33,1:18:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你插到深处
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.41,1:18:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.29,1:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,插到深处
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.37,1:18:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你磨蹭 有顶到子宫吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.31,1:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.32,1:18:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快疯了 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.34,1:19:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.29,1:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你用两个啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.30,1:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 饶了我
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.37,1:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.30,1:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,饶什么饶啊 只是给太太爽而已
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.34,1:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.35,1:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪里啊?要插着逃走吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.36,1:20:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要插着逃走吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.30,1:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要逃去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.30,1:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请饶了我
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.31,1:20:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样逃走吗?这样插着的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.31,1:21:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爱液湿答答的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.33,1:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不行
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.41,1:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不行
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.29,1:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.31,1:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还是真的较好吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.38,1:22:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是真的较好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.32,1:22:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.39,1:22:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要做什么的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.33,1:22:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要拔出这个 插入我的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.34,1:22:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.41,1:22:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,电动阳具咕啾咕啾啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.35,1:22:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.36,1:22:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,给你插入我的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.37,1:23:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.33,1:23:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,用这肉棒让你多去几次啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.40,1:23:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.36,1:23:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.29,1:24:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.31,1:24:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽 过来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.38,1:24:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,过来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.32,1:24:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,过来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.41,1:24:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要洗干净啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.35,1:24:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,洗干净 帮你冲好了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.30,1:25:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吗?这个
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.31,1:25:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.32,1:25:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没这样做过吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.39,1:25:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没有吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.34,1:25:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.34,1:26:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你冲小穴好了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.35,1:26:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.30,1:26:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎样的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.31,1:26:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,被我不停侵犯
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.38,1:26:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎样的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.31,1:26:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.38,1:26:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 好丢脸
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.39,1:26:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.33,1:26:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.40,1:27:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,光手指就湿答答啊你看
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.34,1:27:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了饶了我
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.35,1:27:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起来啊脸
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.29,1:27:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,被我搞到高潮的脸
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.30,1:27:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,用莲蓬头帮你冲啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.32,1:27:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那种地方不行
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.41,1:28:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋了啊 很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.35,1:28:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.32,1:28:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.39,1:28:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.39,1:28:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.33,1:29:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你看啊你那张脸
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.40,1:29:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.38,1:29:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 住手
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.31,1:30:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.41,1:31:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.42,1:31:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃哦 你吃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.35,1:31:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完那个后请你快点回去
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.29,1:31:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,高桥啊 要加班会很晚回来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.36,1:31:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.30,1:31:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一起洗澡啊 帮你刷背
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.37,1:31:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请你回去
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.39,1:32:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.39,1:32:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.33,1:32:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 求你了 快点回来
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.40,1:32:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.40,1:32:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 救我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.34,1:32:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不用讲了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.42,1:32:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别太过分了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.36,1:32:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.30,1:33:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.30,1:33:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这样的啊 要让我生气啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.38,1:33:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.32,1:33:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.33,1:33:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.33,1:33:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.40,1:33:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.34,1:33:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不讨厌吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.35,1:33:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,去夫妻寝室做好了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.36,1:34:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,去寝室啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.31,1:34:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 救命
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.32,1:34:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让我更加兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.40,1:34:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,翘起来了啊我的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.41,1:34:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.36,1:35:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.30,1:35:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让邻居啊 看这样子啊 想丢脸?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.31,1:35:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想丢脸吗?圣子
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.31,1:35:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想再被打?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.39,1:35:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.32,1:35:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢那样的啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.39,1:35:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.32,1:35:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是不是吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.40,1:35:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,跟那家伙平常都睡在这吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.41,1:35:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,更加兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.41,1:35:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.42,1:36:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你再挣扎啊 那样我更兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.29,1:36:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样更爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.30,1:36:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,被侵犯的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.37,1:36:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,被玷污啊 那样较好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.31,1:36:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我 住手
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.32,1:36:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴 让你爽到死为止啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.39,1:36:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.33,1:36:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.41,1:37:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.41,1:37:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我 吃了肉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.35,1:37:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想在夫妻睡的床上SEX
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.35,1:37:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,已经直挺挺 想要我插入吗?肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.29,1:37:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.30,1:37:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.37,1:37:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就说我喜欢听喊不要啊 女人那样子的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.37,1:37:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.39,1:37:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让我舔小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.39,1:37:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.33,1:37:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让我舔小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.33,1:38:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我来让你去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.34,1:38:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.35,1:38:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.37,1:38:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我的脸的话怎样?很难呼吸?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.31,1:38:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.41,1:39:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,被舔小穴啊 高潮不停啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.35,1:39:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知道了啊你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.42,1:39:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.36,1:39:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很好哦...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.30,1:39:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让我喜欢的意思就表示说是那意思啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.37,1:39:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.38,1:39:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很过分啊 不过我想跟你的小穴做
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.32,1:39:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,才来做的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.32,1:40:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你走开啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.39,1:40:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就说啊圣子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.40,1:40:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就看你怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.33,1:40:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.34,1:40:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那没关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.41,1:40:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就算非从这里离开的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.41,1:40:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,照平常那样给我爽
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.29,1:40:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在床上
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.37,1:40:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.33,1:41:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,自己含啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.42,1:41:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别放开啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.37,1:42:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌痛苦的吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.38,1:42:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话就你自己做啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.39,1:42:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在夫妻的床来做啊 服侍
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.39,1:42:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你这一边的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.40,1:42:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不想痛苦吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.40,1:42:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此都闭嘴的就好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.41,1:42:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,用这张嘴多爱抚点啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.36,1:42:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,多舔点 从乳头舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.37,1:43:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一舔吸一吸啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.38,1:43:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.32,1:43:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也握着啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.32,1:43:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.33,1:43:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.34,1:43:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,也吸这边啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.42,1:43:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对 激烈点
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.37,1:44:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢往下面哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.37,1:44:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,到肉棒那边啊 往下面
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.38,1:44:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为圣子很能干啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.39,1:44:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好好含着
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.33,1:44:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没被这样做过吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.33,1:44:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.36,1:45:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的脸嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.37,1:45:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.32,1:45:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,圣子也想要舔啊 是那种脸哦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.39,1:45:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 那来互舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.33,1:45:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股朝这边
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.33,1:45:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的话是绝对啊 小穴这边
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.34,1:46:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡的味道 小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.42,1:46:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃哦小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.29,1:46:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再帮你伸进舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.39,1:46:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想插入小穴了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.33,1:46:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想插入圣子的小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.40,1:46:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,圣子也是吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.40,1:46:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.40,1:46:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,脚张开来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.34,1:47:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.34,1:47:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,又在喊不要不要的 还不是脚张开了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.37,1:47:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.33,1:47:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.42,1:48:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧啊比起平常
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.36,1:48:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.37,1:48:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,打个电话
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.37,1:48:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.37,1:48:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了 高桥辛苦了 是我是我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.38,1:48:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,正努力着吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.38,1:48:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.31,1:48:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊 不是有新企画吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.39,1:48:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.39,1:48:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,挺顺利的
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.39,1:49:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很顺利吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.33,1:49:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.33,1:49:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.33,1:49:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.34,1:49:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?现在 正被你太太请吃饭
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.35,1:49:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.41,1:49:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我换他听啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.35,1:49:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.29,1:49:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.36,1:49:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很忙啊 你太太
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.30,1:49:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.37,1:49:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.37,1:49:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.31,1:49:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的料理也很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.31,1:49:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,肉太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.38,1:49:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,肉吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.38,1:49:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,超多汁的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.38,1:49:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是很软嫩的肉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.39,1:50:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.39,1:50:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很多肉汁
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.39,1:50:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.40,1:50:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你听肉汁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.41,1:50:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真多汁哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.41,1:50:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,加班虽辛苦 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.42,1:50:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,托你的褔 在你家度过很爽快的时间啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.29,1:50:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.36,1:50:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,托你的福 在你家度过很爽快的时间
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.30,1:50:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.37,1:50:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.37,1:50:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.37,1:50:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.38,1:51:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.32,1:51:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很棒吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.33,1:51:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.42,1:51:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.36,1:51:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,圣子 圣子喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.29,1:51:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大概都懂了哦 这个
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.30,1:51:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.30,1:51:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.37,1:52:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,让你多去几次哦在夫妻床上
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.31,1:52:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,牵手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.41,1:52:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你过来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.35,1:52:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再帮你多动点好了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.31,1:53:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你看啊 圣子
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.32,1:53:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你看连成一体了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.41,1:53:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.35,1:53:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,插到深处
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.32,1:54:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很合啊我们俩
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.34,1:54:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉到吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.42,1:55:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.39,1:55:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.39,1:55:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.33,1:55:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.34,1:55:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.37,1:56:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.38,1:57:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啊圣子
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.34,1:58:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,圣子是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.34,1:58:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.41,1:58:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 不要拿下来
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.35,1:58:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.36,1:58:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽 圣子
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.30,1:58:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.37,1:58:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.38,1:58:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.32,1:58:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老公对不起
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.34,2:00:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待 圣子
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.41,2:00:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再来
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.36,2:00:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请别再来了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.37,2:00:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,本片结束
